One issue currently facing a newcomer to bitcoin is, how do I get some? While there is the [[bitcoin_faucet]] or the market place [bitcoin.de](https://www.bitcoin.de/en/registrieren) that can get you started with a small fraction of a coin, when getting larger amounts the user faces an abundance of choice. This page will cut through the clutter, and help direct you to the right exchanger for your needs.

